name: GULP PTB domain containing engulfment adaptor 1
other_names: GULP, engulfment adaptor PTB domain containing 1
summary: The protein encoded by this gene is an adapter protein necessary for the engulfment of apoptotic cells by phagocytes. Several transcript variants, some protein coding and some thought not to be protein coding, have been found for this gene. [provided by RefSeq, Nov 2011].
